OL,3,CWhen is the next Senedd election and
OL,4,Cwhat will be different this time?
OL,6,FWith the 2024 UK General Election
OL,7,Fover, here's everything you need to
OL,8,Fknow about the next Senedd election in
OL,9,FWales:
OL,11,FWhat's the difference between a Senedd
OL,12,Felection and a General Election?
OL,14,FIn a General Election, you're voting
OL,15,Ffor an MP (member of parliament) to
OL,16,Frepresent your local area
OL,17,F(constituency) in the House of Commons
OL,18,Fin Westminster for up to five years.
