OL,3,CWhen is the next Senedd election and
OL,4,Cwhat will be different this time?
OL,6,FThe party that wins the most seats
OL,7,Fwill form the next UK Government and
OL,8,Fits leader will become the prime
OL,9,Fminister. The UK Government is
OL,10,Fresponsible for matters such as
OL,11,Fpolicing, the justice system and
OL,12,Fforeign policy.
OL,14,FIn a Senedd election, similar to a
OL,15,FGeneral Election, you vote for an MS
OL,16,F(member of the Senedd) to represent
OL,17,Fyour area, and the party with the most
OL,18,Fseats will form the next Welsh
OL,19,FGovernment and normally that party's
OL,20,Fleader will become the first minister
OL,21,Fof Wales.
