OL,3,CWhen is the next Senedd election and
OL,4,Cwhat will be different this time?
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government is responsible
OL,7,Ffor devolved issues like health,
OL,8,Feducation, the environment,
OL,9,Fagriculture and housing.
OL,11,FWhen is the next Senedd election?
OL,13,FThe last Senedd election was held on
OL,14,FMay 6, 2021. They normally take place
OL,15,Fonce every five years on the first
OL,16,FThursday in May so we can expect the
OL,17,Fnext Senedd election to take place on
OL,18,FMay 7, 2026.
OL,20,FWill the boundaries be the same as the
OL,21,FGeneral Election?
