OL,3,CWhen is the next Senedd election and
OL,4,Cwhat will be different this time?
OL,6,FMany Westminster seats radically
OL,7,Fchanged for the 2024 General Election,
OL,8,Fwith the number of MPs in Wales cut
OL,9,Ffrom 40 to 32. All but one
OL,10,Fconstituency boundary in Wales was
OL,11,Fredrawn, except for Ynys Mon.
OL,13,FIn the next Senedd election, MSs will
OL,14,Fbe elected from 16 new constituencies
OL,15,Fmade by pairing the 32 Westminster
OL,16,Fseats. There will be a boundary review
OL,17,Fafter the 2026 election.
OL,19,FHow will the new voting system work?
