OL,3,CWhen is the next Senedd election and
OL,4,Cwhat will be different this time?
OL,6,FThe voting system will also change for
OL,7,Fthe next Senedd election. This time,
OL,8,Fvoters will be able to back a
OL,9,Fpolitical party, rather than a
OL,10,Fcandidate.
OL,12,FFor previous Senedd elections, the
OL,13,Fadditional member system has been used
OL,14,Fto elect the MSs. In the past, the
OL,15,Fpublic have had two votes. The first
OL,16,Fvote has been used to elect 40 of the
OL,17,FSenedd members by using a Westminster-
OL,18,Fstyle first-past-the-post electoral
OL,19,Fsystem. The second vote has been to
OL,20,Felect the other 20 regional members by
OL,21,Fchoosing a political party.
