OL,3,CWhen is the next Senedd election and
OL,4,Cwhat will be different this time?
OL,6,FFrom 2026, you will only have one vote
OL,7,Fand the electoral system will be
OL,8,Fchanged to use the D'hondt formula.
OL,9,FIt's a system which is based on the
OL,10,Fprinciple of proportional
OL,11,Frepresentation.
OL,13,FThere will be 96 Senedd members in
OL,14,Ftotal, with each of the 16
OL,15,Fconstituencies represented by six
OL,16,Fmembers.
