OL,3,CWhen is the next Senedd election and
OL,4,Cwhat will be different this time?
OL,6,FUnless voting for an independent
OL,7,Fcandidate, people will choose a
OL,8,Fpolitical party to vote for, with the
OL,9,Felected representatives coming from
OL,10,Flists decided by parties. The names of
OL,11,Fall candidates will appear on the
OL,12,Fballot paper.
OL,14,FWhat are the plans for gender quotas?
OL,16,FIn 2003, Wales became the first
OL,17,Fcountry in the world to elect women in
OL,18,F50% of its parliament's seats. Over
OL,19,Fthe last two decades, that proportion
OL,20,Fhas fallen.
